                    </div>
                    <h2 class="text-4xl font-black text-white mb-4 slide-fade leading-tight">Exploraste <span class="text-emerald-300">{uniqueEpisodes}</span> episodios únicos</h2>
                    <div class="bg-black/20 backdrop-blur-md rounded-2xl p-6 slide-fade-up border border-white/20 mt-6">
